{"word":"Feasts","slug":"feasts","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Feasts</b> Ancient customs at:<br/> - Men alone present at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=40&verse=20'>Gen 40:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=43&verse=32'>Gen 43:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=43&verse=34'>Gen 43:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=9&verse=22'>1Sa 9:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=1&verse=9'>Est 1:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=6&verse=21'>Mar 6:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=14&verse=24'>Luk 14:24</a> <br/> - Men and women attend<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=32&verse=6'>Exo 32:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=32&verse=3'>Exo 32:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=5&verse=3'>Dan 5:3</a> <br/> - Riddles propounded at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=14&verse=12'>Jdg 14:12</a> <br/> - Marriage feasts provided by the bridegroom<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=14&verse=10'>Jdg 14:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=14&verse=17'>Jdg 14:17</a> <br/> - Guests arranged according to age<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=43&verse=33'>Gen 43:33</a> <br/> - Guests arranged according to rank<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=9&verse=22'>1Sa 9:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=14&verse=10'>Luk 14:10</a> <br/> - Reclined on couches<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=6&verse=4'>Amo 6:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=6&verse=7'>Amo 6:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=7&verse=38'>Luk 7:38</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=13&verse=25'>Joh 13:25</a> <br/> - Served in one dish<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=23'>Mat 26:23</a> <br/> - Were presided over by a governor<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=2&verse=9'>Joh 2:9</a> <br/> - Host served<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=18&verse=8'>Gen 18:8</a> <br/> - Wine served at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=5&verse=6'>Est 5:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=7&verse=7'>Est 7:7</a> <br/> - Music at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=5&verse=12'>Isa 5:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=6&verse=5'>Amo 6:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=15&verse=25'>Luk 15:25</a> <br/> - Dancing at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=14&verse=6'>Mat 14:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=15&verse=25'>Luk 15:25</a> <br/> - Given by kings<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=20&verse=5'>1Sa 20:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=25&verse=36'>1Sa 25:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=9&verse=10'>2Sa 9:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=2&verse=7'>1Ki 2:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=4&verse=22'>1Ki 4:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=18&verse=19'>1Ki 18:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=1&verse=8'>Est 1:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=5&verse=4'>Dan 5:4</a> <br/> Drunkenness at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=25&verse=36'>1Sa 25:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=1&verse=10'>Est 1:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=5&verse=4'>Dan 5:4</a><br/> Covenants ratified by<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=26&verse=30'>Gen 26:30</a><br/> Celebrations for:<br/> - Birthdays<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=40&verse=20'>Gen 40:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=6&verse=21'>Mar 6:21</a> <br/> - Coronations<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=1&verse=25'>1Ki 1:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=12&verse=40'>1Ch 12:40</a> <br/> - National deliverances<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=8&verse=17'>Est 8:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=9&verse=19'>Est 9:19</a> <br/> Figurative<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=22&verse=14'>Mat 22:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=14&verse=24'>Luk 14:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=19&verse=9'>Rev 19:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=19&verse=17'>Rev 19:17</a><br/> Annual festivals instituted by Moses:<br/> - Designated as:<br/> b Solemn Feasts<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=15&verse=3'>Num 15:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=8&verse=13'>2Ch 8:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=25&chapter=2&verse=6'>Lam 2:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=46&verse=9'>Eze 46:9</a><br/> b Set Feasts<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=29&verse=39'>Num 29:39</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=3&verse=5'>Ezr 3:5</a><br/> b Appointed Feasts<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=1&verse=14'>Isa 1:14</a><br/> b Holy Convocations<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=23&verse=4'>Lev 23:4</a><br/> - First and last days were Sabbatic<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=23&verse=40'>Lev 23:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=28&verse=25'>Num 28:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=29&verse=12'>Num 29:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=29&verse=35'>Num 29:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=8&verse=18'>Neh 8:18</a> <br/> - Kept with rejoicing<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=23&verse=40'>Lev 23:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=16&verse=14'>Deu 16:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=30&verse=26'>2Ch 30:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=6&verse=22'>Ezr 6:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=8&verse=12'>Neh 8:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=8&verse=17'>Neh 8:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=42&verse=4'>Psa 42:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=122&verse=4'>Psa 122:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=30&verse=29'>Isa 30:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=8&verse=19'>Zec 8:19</a> <br/> - Divine protection given during<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=34&verse=24'>Exo 34:24</a> <br/> - The three principal festivals were Passover, Pentecost, Tabernacles:<br/> b All males were required to attend<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=23&verse=17'>Exo 23:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=34&verse=23'>Exo 34:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=16&verse=16'>Deu 16:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=42&verse=4'>Psa 42:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=122&verse=4'>Psa 122:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=36&verse=38'>Eze 36:38</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=44'>Luk 2:44</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=4&verse=45'>Joh 4:45</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=7'>Joh 7</a><br/> b Aliens permitted to attend<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=12&verse=20'>Joh 12:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=2&verse=11'>Act 2:11</a><br/> b Attended by women<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=1&verse=3'>1Sa 1:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=1&verse=9'>1Sa 1:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=41'>Luk 2:41</a><br/> b Observed:<br/> b by Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=20'>Mat 26:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=42'>Luk 2:42</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=22&verse=15'>Luk 22:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=2&verse=13'>Joh 2:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=2&verse=23'>Joh 2:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=5&verse=1'>Joh 5:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=7&verse=10'>Joh 7:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=10&verse=22'>Joh 10:22</a><br/> b by Paul<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=18&verse=21'>Act 18:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=19&verse=21'>Act 19:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=20&verse=6'>Act 20:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=20&verse=16'>Act 20:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=24&verse=11'>Act 24:11</a>; <a href='https://w